base <- read.csv('C:/Users/lucas.general/Documents/Documentos R Markdown/Comportamento/Promos_Semanais/Promos_Semanais.CSV', encoding = "UTF-8")

base <- base %>% 
  rename(pk_customer = X.U.FEFF.pk_customer)


base <- base %>% 
  group_by(pk_customer) %>% 
  summarise(pedidos = sum(purchase)) %>% 
  inner_join(base, by ='pk_customer') %>% 
    mutate(pedidos2 = ifelse(pedidos == 0, 'Sem compra',
                           ifelse(pedidos == 1, 'Uma compra',
                                  ifelse(pedidos == 2, 'Duas compras',
                                         'Mais que duas compras'))))



base <- base %>% 
  filter(purchase > 0) %>% 
  group_by(pk_customer) %>% 
  summarise(Prim_compra = min(visitas)) %>% 
  right_join(base, by = 'pk_customer')

base <- base %>% 
  mutate(is_weekly_campaign = ifelse(is_weekly_campaign == -1,0,is_weekly_campaign),
         is_image_search = ifelse(is_image_search == -1,0,is_image_search),
         is_fit_finder = ifelse(is_fit_finder == -1,0,is_fit_finder)) %>% 
  mutate_if(is.numeric, replace_na, 0)
g_legend<-function(a.gplot){
  tmp <- ggplot_gtable(ggplot_build(a.gplot))
  leg <- which(sapply(tmp$grobs, function(x) x$name) == "guide-box")
  legend <- tmp$grobs[[leg]]
  return(legend)}

base <- base %>% 
  mutate(pedidos2 = factor(pedidos2, levels = c('Sem compra', 'Uma compra', 'Duas compras', 'Mais que duas compras')))

Clientes com primeira visita entre 2020-11-01 e 2020-11-10

Comportamentos

resumo <- base %>% 
  group_by(pk_customer) %>% 
  summarise(is_weekly_campaign = max(is_weekly_campaign),
            is_image_search = max(is_image_search),
            is_fit_finder = max(is_fit_finder)) %>% 
  ungroup() %>% 
  summarise(is_weekly_campaign = sum(is_weekly_campaign),
            is_image_search = sum(is_image_search),
            is_fit_finder = sum(is_fit_finder),
            clientes = n())

num_clientes <- as.integer(resumo %>% 
  select(clientes))


resumo2 <-base %>% 
  filter(is_weekly_campaign > 0) %>% 
  group_by(pk_customer) %>% 
  summarise(is_weekly_campaign = sum(is_weekly_campaign),
            prim_visita_WC = min(visitas)) %>% 
  full_join(base %>% 
              filter(is_image_search > 0) %>% 
              group_by(pk_customer) %>% 
              summarise(is_image_search = sum(is_image_search),
                        prim_visita_IS = min(visitas)),
            by = 'pk_customer')%>% 
  full_join(base %>% 
              filter(is_fit_finder > 0) %>% 
              group_by(pk_customer) %>% 
              summarise(is_fit_finder = sum(is_fit_finder),
                        prim_visita_FF = min(visitas)),
            by = 'pk_customer')



resumo3 <- resumo2 %>% 
  filter(is_image_search > 0) %>% 
  summarise(is_image_search = median(is_image_search)) %>% 
  mutate(um = 1) %>% 
  inner_join(
    resumo2 %>% 
      filter(is_fit_finder > 0) %>% 
      summarise(is_fit_finder = median(is_fit_finder)) %>% 
      mutate(um = 1),
    by = 'um'
  ) %>% 
  inner_join(
    resumo2 %>% 
      filter(is_weekly_campaign > 0) %>% 
      summarise(is_weekly_campaign = median(is_weekly_campaign))%>% 
      mutate(um = 1),
    by = 'um'
    ) %>% 
  select(is_image_search,is_fit_finder,is_weekly_campaign)

resumo2 <- resumo3 %>% 
  union_all(
    resumo2 %>% 
      filter(is_image_search > 0) %>% 
      summarise(is_image_search = median(prim_visita_IS)) %>% 
      mutate(um = 1) %>% 
      inner_join(
        resumo2 %>% 
          filter(is_fit_finder > 0) %>% 
          summarise(is_fit_finder = median(prim_visita_FF)) %>% 
          mutate(um = 1),
        by = 'um'
      ) %>% 
      inner_join(
        resumo2 %>% 
          filter(is_weekly_campaign > 0) %>% 
          summarise(is_weekly_campaign = median(prim_visita_WC))%>% 
          mutate(um = 1),
        by = 'um'
        ) %>% 
      select(is_image_search,is_fit_finder,is_weekly_campaign) 
    )

resumo <- resumo %>% 
  select(-clientes) %>% 
  union_all(resumo2) %>% 
  t()

resumo <- as.data.frame(resumo)


resumo$comportamento <- rownames(resumo)

rownames(resumo) <- NULL

resumo %>% 
  rename(Quantidade_Clientes = V1,
         Mediana_usos = V2,
         Primeiro_uso = V3) %>% 
  mutate(porcentagem = Quantidade_Clientes/num_clientes,
         porcentagem = paste(round(porcentagem*100,2),'%',sep='')) %>% 
  select(comportamento, Quantidade_Clientes,porcentagem,Mediana_usos,Primeiro_uso) %>% 
  knitr::kable() %>%

freq <- base %>% 
  filter(is_weekly_campaign > 0) %>% 
  group_by(pk_customer) %>% 
  summarise(Prim_visitas = min(visitas)) %>% 
  inner_join(base, by = 'pk_customer') %>% 
  mutate(flag_pos = ifelse(visitas < Prim_visitas, 0,1)) %>% 
  filter(Prim_visitas >= 3)
  

freq <- freq %>% 
  filter(flag_pos == 0) %>% 
  mutate(id_date = as.character(id_date),
         id_date = as.Date(id_date,'%Y%m%d')) %>% 
  group_by(pk_customer) %>% 
  summarise(max_date = max(id_date),
            min_date = min(id_date),
            visitas = length(unique(id_date))) %>% 
  mutate(diff_date = max_date-min_date,
         diff_date = as.integer(diff_date)+1,
         diff_date = diff_date/30,
         freq_visita_mes_pre = visitas/diff_date) %>% 
  select(pk_customer, freq_visita_mes_pre) %>% 
  left_join(
    freq %>% 
      filter(flag_pos == 1) %>% 
      mutate(id_date = as.character(id_date),
             id_date = as.Date(id_date,'%Y%m%d')) %>% 
      group_by(pk_customer) %>% 
      summarise(max_date = max(Sys.Date()),
                min_date = min(id_date),
                visitas = length(unique(id_date))) %>% 
      mutate(diff_date = max_date-min_date,
             diff_date = as.integer(diff_date)+1,
             diff_date = diff_date/30,
             freq_visita_mes_pos = visitas/diff_date) %>% 
      select(pk_customer, freq_visita_mes_pos),
    by = 'pk_customer'
    ) %>% 
  mutate(diff_freq_visita = freq_visita_mes_pos/freq_visita_mes_pre)


freq %>% 
  summarise(qtd_clientes = n(),
            Mediana_freq_visita_pre = median(freq_visita_mes_pre),
            Mediana_freq_visita_pos = median(freq_visita_mes_pos),
            Mediana_diff_freq_visita = Mediana_freq_visita_pos/Mediana_freq_visita_pre - 1,
            Mediana_diff_freq_visita = paste(round(Mediana_diff_freq_visita*100,2), '%', sep = '')
            ) %>% 
  mutate(Mediana_freq_visita_pre = round(Mediana_freq_visita_pre,2),
         Mediana_freq_visita_pos = round(Mediana_freq_visita_pos,2)) %>% 
  knitr::kable(caption = "Diferena na frequencia de visitas de clientes com campanhas semanais") %>%  
  kable_styling()

Clientes que tiveram antes da primeira compra

clientes <- base %>% 
  filter(is_weekly_campaign > 0) %>% 
  group_by(pk_customer) %>% 
  summarise(prim_visitas = min(visitas)) %>% 
  right_join(base, by = 'pk_customer') %>% 
  group_by(pk_customer,prim_visitas,Prim_compra,pedidos2) %>% 
  summarise(max_visitas = max(visitas)) %>% 
  mutate(flag = ifelse(prim_visitas <= Prim_compra | (Prim_compra == 0 & !is.na(prim_visitas)),'Antes da Primeira compra','Sem Evento ou ps compra')) %>% 
  mutate_if(is.character, replace_na, 'Sem Evento ou ps compra')
  
clientes %>% 
  ggplot() +
  geom_bar(aes(x=flag, fill=pedidos2))+
  labs(#title = "Pedidos por periodo primeira visita na Home",
        x = "Periodo",
        y = "Contagem",
        caption = "",
        colour = ""
       )+
  theme(legend.position="bottom")

plot1 <- clientes %>% 
  ggplot() +
  geom_bar(aes(x=flag, fill=pedidos2), position = 'fill')+
  scale_y_continuous(labels = scales::percent_format(), breaks = seq(0,1, by = 0.25))+
  labs(#title = "Pedidos por periodo primeira visita na Home",
        subtitle = "Total",
        x = "Periodo",
        y = "Porcentagem",
        caption = "",
        colour = ""
       )+
  theme(legend.position="bottom")
x <- clientes %>% 
  filter(flag == 'Sem Evento ou ps compra' ) %>% 
  group_by(max_visitas) %>% 
  summarise(clientes1 = n()) %>% 
  inner_join(
    clientes %>% 
      filter(flag == 'Antes da Primeira compra') %>% 
      group_by(max_visitas) %>% 
      summarise(clientes2 = n()),
    by = 'max_visitas'
  ) %>% 
  mutate(menor = pmin(clientes1,clientes2))

clientes <- clientes %>% 
  inner_join(x %>% 
               select(max_visitas, menor),
             by = 'max_visitas') %>% 
  group_by(flag, max_visitas) %>% 
  mutate(id = row_number()) %>% 
  filter(id <= menor) 


plot2 <- clientes %>% 
  ggplot() +
  geom_bar(aes(x=flag, fill=pedidos2), position = 'fill')+
  scale_y_continuous(labels = scales::percent_format(), breaks = seq(0,1, by = 0.25))+
  labs(#title = "Pedidos por periodo primeira visita na Home",
        subtitle = "UnderSampling qtd de visitas",
        x = "Periodo",
        y = "Porcentagem",
        caption = "",
        colour = ""
       )+
  theme(legend.position="bottom")


mylegend<-g_legend(plot1)

grid.arrange(arrangeGrob(plot1 + theme(legend.position="none"),
                         plot2 + theme(legend.position="none"),
                         top = 'Pedidos por periodo primeira visita na weekly Campaign',
                         nrow=1),
             mylegend, nrow=2,heights=c(10, 1))

clientes <- base %>% 
  filter(is_weekly_campaign > 0) %>% 
  group_by(pk_customer) %>% 
  summarise(qtd_usos = n()) %>% 
  right_join(base, by = 'pk_customer') %>% 
  group_by(pk_customer,qtd_usos,pedidos2) %>% 
  summarise(max_visitas = max(visitas)) %>% 
  mutate(porcentagem_uso = qtd_usos/max_visitas) %>% 
  mutate_if(is.numeric, replace_na, 0)
  
clientes <- clientes %>% 
  ungroup() %>% 
  mutate(qtd_usos = ifelse(porcentagem_uso == 1, 'Todas as vezes',
                           ifelse(porcentagem_uso == 0, 'Nenhum uso',
                                  'Entre 0 e 100%')))

clientes %>% 
  ggplot() +
  geom_bar(aes(x=qtd_usos, fill=pedidos2))+
  labs(#title = "Pedidos por periodo primeira visita na Home",
        x = "Quantidade de usos",
        y = "Contagem",
        caption = "",
        colour = ""
       )+
  theme(legend.position="bottom")

  labs(#title = "Pedidos por periodo primeira visita na Home",
        subtitle = "Total",
        x = "Quantidade de usos",
        y = "Porcentagem",
        caption = "",
        colour = ""
       )+
  theme(legend.position="bottom")
x <- clientes %>% 
  filter(qtd_usos == 'Entre 0 e 100%' ) %>% 
  group_by(max_visitas) %>% 
  summarise(clientes1 = n()) %>% 
  inner_join(
    clientes %>% 
      filter(qtd_usos == 'Nenhum uso') %>% 
      group_by(max_visitas) %>% 
      summarise(clientes2 = n()),
    by = 'max_visitas'
  ) %>% 
  mutate(menor = pmin(clientes1,clientes2))

clientes <- clientes %>% 
  inner_join(x %>% 
               select(max_visitas, menor),
             by = 'max_visitas') %>% 
  group_by(qtd_usos, max_visitas) %>% 
  mutate(id = row_number()) %>% 
  filter(id <= menor)

  ggplot() +

  scale_y_continuous(labels = scales::percent_format(), breaks = seq(0,1, by = 0.25))+
  labs(#title = "Pedidos por periodo primeira visita na Home",
        subtitle = "Total",

Utilizacao

freq <- base %>% 
  filter(is_fit_finder > 0) %>% 
  group_by(pk_customer) %>% 
  summarise(Prim_visitas = min(visitas)) %>% 
  inner_join(base, by = 'pk_customer') %>% 
  mutate(flag_pos = ifelse(visitas < Prim_visitas, 0,1)) %>% 
  filter(Prim_visitas >= 3)
  

freq <- freq %>% 
  filter(flag_pos == 0) %>% 
  mutate(id_date = as.character(id_date),
         id_date = as.Date(id_date,'%Y%m%d')) %>% 
  group_by(pk_customer) %>% 
  summarise(max_date = max(id_date),
            min_date = min(id_date),
            visitas = length(unique(id_date))) %>% 
  mutate(diff_date = max_date-min_date,
         diff_date = as.integer(diff_date)+1,
         diff_date = diff_date/30,
         freq_visita_mes_pre = visitas/diff_date) %>% 
  select(pk_customer, freq_visita_mes_pre) %>% 
  inner_join(
    freq %>% 
      filter(flag_pos == 1) %>% 
      mutate(id_date = as.character(id_date),
             id_date = as.Date(id_date,'%Y%m%d')) %>% 
      group_by(pk_customer) %>% 
      summarise(max_date = max(Sys.Date()),
                min_date = min(id_date),
                visitas = length(unique(id_date))) %>% 
      mutate(diff_date = max_date-min_date,
             diff_date = as.integer(diff_date)+1,
             diff_date = diff_date/30,
             freq_visita_mes_pos = visitas/diff_date) %>% 
      select(pk_customer, freq_visita_mes_pos),
    by = 'pk_customer'
    ) %>% 
  mutate(diff_freq_visita = freq_visita_mes_pos/freq_visita_mes_pre)


freq %>% 
  summarise(qtd_clientes = n(),
            Mediana_freq_visita_pre = median(freq_visita_mes_pre),
            Mediana_freq_visita_pos = median(freq_visita_mes_pos),
            Mediana_diff_freq_visita = Mediana_freq_visita_pos/Mediana_freq_visita_pre - 1,
            Mediana_diff_freq_visita = paste(round(Mediana_diff_freq_visita*100,2), '%', sep = '')
            ) %>% 
  mutate(Mediana_freq_visita_pre = round(Mediana_freq_visita_pre,2),
         Mediana_freq_visita_pos = round(Mediana_freq_visita_pos,2)) %>% 
  knitr::kable(caption = "Diferena na frequencia de visitas de clientes com Fit Finder") %>%  
  kable_styling()

7295 10 2.95 -70.49%
